      data:
        difficulty: 0
        question:
        - This force is the difference between the applied force and the countering
          force. Which of the following best describes this?
        - This force is what separates the applied force from the opposing force.
          Which of the following best describes this?
        - This force differentiates the applied force from the opposing force. Which
          of the following best describes this?
        correctAnswer:
        - Net Force
        wrongAnswers:
